title: People's Court: The Case of Jenny Not Drinking AS MUCH
description: Dave, Falen, and listener Heidi take Jenny to court about the fact that she CLAIMS she doesn't really drink anymore but then comes in every Monday with stories from the weekend that involve drinking.
